Sentencas: A new cubic double perovskite oxide, LaSrMnCoO5+delta(LSMC), was investigated as a novel cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFC).
Titulo: LaSrMnCoO5+δ as cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity of an LSMC sample reaches 111-140 S cm(-1) in the temperature range 600-850 degrees C. XRD results show that an LSMC cathode is chemically compatible with IT electrolyte material Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9 (SDC).
Titulo: LaSrMnCoO5+δ as cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The interfacial polarization resistance was as low as 0.048, 0.098 and 0.219 Omega cm(2) at 800, 750, and 700 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: LaSrMnCoO5+δ as cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The preliminary results suggested that double perovskite LSMC material could be considered as the candidate for IT-SOFC cathode.
Titulo: LaSrMnCoO5+δ as cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
